{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2014,"text":"When I think about dreams,"},{"time":4000,"text":"like many of you,"},{"time":5900,"text":"I think about this picture."},{"time":8838,"text":"I was eight when I watched Neil Armstrong"},{"time":12899,"text":"step off the Lunar Module\nonto the surface of the Moon."},{"time":17454,"text":"I had never seen anything like it before,"},{"time":20708,"text":"and I've never seen\nanything like it since."}]},{"cues":[{"time":24319,"text":"We got to the Moon for one simple reason:"},{"time":28637,"text":"John Kennedy committed us to a deadline."},{"time":32978,"text":"And in the absence of that deadline,"},{"time":35494,"text":"we would still be dreaming about it."},{"time":39209,"text":"Leonard Bernstein said two things\nare necessary for great achievement:"},{"time":43901,"text":"a plan and not quite enough time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":47390,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":51851,"text":"Deadlines and commitments"},{"time":56369,"text":"are the great and fading\nlessons of Apollo."},{"time":62514,"text":"And they are what give the word\n\"moonshot\" its meaning."},{"time":67498,"text":"And our world is in desperate need\nof political leaders"},{"time":72244,"text":"willing to set bold deadlines"},{"time":76053,"text":"for the achievement of daring dreams\non the scale of Apollo again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":82368,"text":"When I think about dreams,"},{"time":83885,"text":"I think about the drag queens\nof LA and Stonewall"},{"time":87958,"text":"and millions of other people\nrisking everything"},{"time":90331,"text":"to come out when that\nwas really dangerous,"},{"time":93667,"text":"and of this picture of the White House\nlit up in rainbow colors,"},{"time":97412,"text":"yes --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":98594,"text":"(Applause) --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":104397,"text":"celebrating America's gay and lesbian\ncitizens' right to marry."},{"time":107909,"text":"It is a picture that in my wildest dreams\nI could never have imagined"},{"time":112180,"text":"when I was 18"},{"time":114932,"text":"and figuring out that I was gay"},{"time":117956,"text":"and feeling estranged from my country"},{"time":121647,"text":"and my dreams because of it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":125956,"text":"I think about this picture of my family"},{"time":129234,"text":"that I never dreamed I could ever have --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":133281,"text":"(Applause) --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":139141,"text":"and of our children holding this headline"},{"time":142091,"text":"I never dreamed could ever be printed\nabout the Supreme Court ruling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":148517,"text":"We need more of the courage\nof drag queens and astronauts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":154319,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":156669,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":159366,"text":"But I want to talk\nabout the need for us to dream"},{"time":162732,"text":"in more than one dimension,"},{"time":164842,"text":"because there was something about Apollo\nthat I didn't know when I was 8,"},{"time":170272,"text":"and something about organizing\nthat the rainbow colors over."},{"time":175699,"text":"Of the 30 astronauts in the original\nMercury, Gemini and Apollo programs,"},{"time":180802,"text":"only seven marriages survived."},{"time":185699,"text":"Those iconic images of the astronauts\nbouncing on the Moon"},{"time":189498,"text":"obscure the alcoholism\nand depression on Earth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":194907,"text":"Thomas Merton, the Trappist monk,"},{"time":197541,"text":"asked during the time of Apollo,"},{"time":199980,"text":"\"What can we gain by sailing to the moon"},{"time":203920,"text":"if we are not able to cross the abyss\nthat separates us from ourselves?\""},{"time":211561,"text":"And what can we gain by the right to marry"},{"time":214396,"text":"if we are not able to cross the acrimony"},{"time":217563,"text":"and emotional distance\nthat so often separates us from our love?"},{"time":222596,"text":"And not just in marriage."},{"time":225120,"text":"I have seen the most hurtful, destructive,"},{"time":232231,"text":"tragic infighting in LGBT and AIDS"},{"time":236453,"text":"and breast cancer and non-profit activism,"},{"time":239873,"text":"all in the name of love."}]},{"cues":[{"time":242898,"text":"Thomas Merton also wrote\nabout wars among saints"},{"time":247639,"text":"and that \"there is a pervasive form\nof contemporary violence"},{"time":253692,"text":"to which the idealist\nmost easily succumbs:"},{"time":258065,"text":"activism and overwork."},{"time":261414,"text":"The frenzy of our activism\nneutralizes our work for peace."},{"time":266215,"text":"It destroys our own\ninner capacity for peace.\""},{"time":272041,"text":"Too often our dreams become\nthese compartmentalized fixations"},{"time":277526,"text":"on some future"},{"time":279383,"text":"that destroy our ability to be present\nfor our lives right now."},{"time":284926,"text":"Our dreams of a better life\nfor some future humanity"},{"time":288665,"text":"or some other humanity in another country"},{"time":290949,"text":"alienate us from the beautiful\nhuman beings sitting next to us"},{"time":294997,"text":"at this very moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":298481,"text":"Well, that's just the price\nof progress, we say."},{"time":301664,"text":"You can go to the Moon"},{"time":303101,"text":"or you can have stability\nin your family life."},{"time":307679,"text":"And we can't conceive of dreaming\nin both dimensions at the same time."},{"time":312012,"text":"And we don't set the bar\nmuch higher than stability"},{"time":315801,"text":"when it comes to our emotional life."},{"time":318579,"text":"Which is why our technology\nfor talking to one another"},{"time":321939,"text":"has gone vertical,"},{"time":324332,"text":"our ability to listen\nand understand one another"},{"time":328062,"text":"has gone nowhere."},{"time":331236,"text":"Our access to information\nis through the roof,"},{"time":335665,"text":"our access to joy, grounded."},{"time":341442,"text":"But this idea, that our present\nand our future are mutually exclusive,"},{"time":347338,"text":"that to fulfill our potential for doing\nwe have to surrender"},{"time":351358,"text":"our profound potential for being,"},{"time":354545,"text":"that the number of transistors\non a circuit can be doubled and doubled,"},{"time":358480,"text":"but our capacity for compassion\nand humanity and serenity and love"},{"time":362806,"text":"is somehow limited"},{"time":364908,"text":"is a false and suffocating choice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":370237,"text":"Now, I'm not suggesting"},{"time":372073,"text":"simply the uninspiring idea\nof more work-life balance."},{"time":379541,"text":"What good is it for me to spend\nmore time with my kids at home"},{"time":382478,"text":"if my mind is always somewhere else\nwhile I'm doing it?"},{"time":386600,"text":"I'm not even talking about mindfulness."},{"time":388589,"text":"Mindfulness is all of a sudden becoming\na tool for improving productivity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":393973,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":396314,"text":"Right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":397490,"text":"I'm talking about dreaming"},{"time":400458,"text":"as boldly in the dimension of our being"},{"time":405243,"text":"as we do about industry and technology."},{"time":407751,"text":"I'm talking about\nan audacious authenticity"},{"time":412536,"text":"that allows us to cry with one another,"},{"time":416298,"text":"a heroic humility that allows us\nto remove our masks and be real."},{"time":421850,"text":"It is our inability\nto be with one another,"},{"time":424399,"text":"our fear of crying with one another,\nthat gives rise to so many"},{"time":428757,"text":"of the problems we are frantically\ntrying to solve in the first place,"},{"time":432075,"text":"from Congressional gridlock\nto economic inhumanity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":436097,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":439388,"text":"I'm talking about what Jonas Salk\ncalled an Epoch B,"},{"time":443459,"text":"a new epoch in which we become\nas excited about and curious about"},{"time":449094,"text":"and scientific about\nthe development of our humanity"},{"time":453127,"text":"as we are about the development\nof our technology."}]},{"cues":[{"time":457341,"text":"We should not shrink from this opportunity"},{"time":459826,"text":"simply because\nwe don't really understand it."},{"time":463357,"text":"There was a time\nwhen we didn't understand space."},{"time":466722,"text":"Or because we're more used\nto technology and activism."},{"time":470174,"text":"That is the very definition\nof being stuck in a comfort zone."},{"time":473469,"text":"We are now very comfortable imagining\nunimaginable technological achievement."},{"time":479842,"text":"In 2016, it is the dimension\nof our being itself"},{"time":484017,"text":"that cries out for its fair share\nof our imagination."}]},{"cues":[{"time":491782,"text":"Now, we're all here to dream,"},{"time":494131,"text":"but maybe if we're honest about it,"},{"time":495823,"text":"each of us chasing our own dream."},{"time":498536,"text":"You know, looking at the name tags\nto see who can help me with my dream,"},{"time":502330,"text":"sometimes looking right through\none another's humanity."},{"time":505450,"text":"I can't be bothered with you right now.\nI have an idea for saving the world."},{"time":509513,"text":"Right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":510689,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":513830,"text":"Years ago, once upon a time,\nI had this beautiful company"},{"time":518330,"text":"that created these long journeys\nfor heroic civic engagement."},{"time":522647,"text":"And we had this mantra:"},{"time":524718,"text":"\"Human. Kind. Be Both.\""},{"time":529139,"text":"And we encouraged people to experiment\noutrageously with kindness."},{"time":535599,"text":"Like, \"Go help everybody\nset up their tents.\""},{"time":539400,"text":"And there were a lot of tents."}]},{"cues":[{"time":541995,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":544043,"text":"\"Go buy everybody Popsicles.\""},{"time":545790,"text":"\"Go help people fix their flat tires"},{"time":547695,"text":"even though you know\nthe dinner line is going to get longer.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":550645,"text":"And people really took us up on this,"},{"time":553043,"text":"so much so that if you got\na flat tire on the AIDS ride,"},{"time":555694,"text":"you had trouble fixing it, because there\nwere so many people there asking you"},{"time":559345,"text":"if you needed help."}]},{"cues":[{"time":561345,"text":"For a few days,\nfor tens of thousands of people,"},{"time":565378,"text":"we created these worlds"},{"time":567316,"text":"that everybody said were the way\nthey wish the world could always be."},{"time":574316,"text":"What if we experimented\nwith creating that kind of world"},{"time":578847,"text":"these next few days?"},{"time":582156,"text":"And instead of going up to someone\nand asking them, \"What do you do?\""},{"time":587195,"text":"ask them, \"So what are your dreams?\""},{"time":590315,"text":"or \"What are your broken dreams?\""},{"time":593346,"text":"You know, \"TED.\"\nTend to Each other's Dreams."}]},{"cues":[{"time":598830,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":603623,"text":"Maybe it's \"I want to stay sober\""},{"time":606203,"text":"or \"I want to build\na tree house with my kid.\""},{"time":609512,"text":"You know, instead of going up\nto the person everybody wants to meet,"},{"time":612728,"text":"go up to the person who is all alone"},{"time":614509,"text":"and ask them if they want\nto grab a cup of coffee."}]},{"cues":[{"time":618544,"text":"I think what we fear most"},{"time":621044,"text":"is that we will be denied the opportunity\nto fulfill our true potential,"},{"time":625424,"text":"that we are born to dream"},{"time":628059,"text":"and we might die\nwithout ever having the chance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":633630,"text":"Imagine living in a world"},{"time":635282,"text":"where we simply recognize\nthat deep, existential fear in one another"},{"time":641503,"text":"and love one another boldly\nbecause we know"},{"time":644659,"text":"that to be human\nis to live with that fear."},{"time":649793,"text":"It's time for us to dream\nin multiple dimensions simultaneously,"},{"time":656262,"text":"and somewhere that transcends\nall of the wondrous things"},{"time":660254,"text":"we can and will and must do"},{"time":664881,"text":"lies the domain of all\nthe unbelievable things we could be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":671748,"text":"It's time we set foot into that dimension"},{"time":675230,"text":"and came out about the fact\nthat we have dreams there, too."},{"time":681214,"text":"If the Moon could dream,"},{"time":686039,"text":"I think that would be its dream for us."},{"time":691540,"text":"It's an honor to be with you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":693203,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":695136,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}